This map is a realistic map: have no teleports or false walls.
The map is based on a big building in the city. That building is a police dept with jails. The playable floors are 4 plus the roof.

This jail map have got interactive ducts, football, pool with disco, nursery, jails, isolation jail, kitchen, toilets, and armory. There are some weapons all over the map for the terrorists.

A lot of escape ways are by the windows. Example: you can jump by the window near the jails an do surf in the oblique roof to reach the pool.

In the jails there are 3 smokes, 1 pistol, and 1 hegrenade.

The song of the disco is a remix of We No Speak Americano.

There are 25 slots for Ts and 24 for CTs.

Hope you like it.

Leave comments please!

Created by Captain Nighthawk


This map was originally a small scheme, but it was abandoned so I decided to take it on. I turned the map into a concrete/modern themed jail map.

It was designed for the Ct's to be able to have full control over the t's.
The map is currently being played on the Edgegamers Jailbreak server and does not lag with 40 players on.
There are 20 Ct Spawns and 40 T Spawns, this version was created for Edgegamers, but different versions can be arranged if you notify me.

**This map requires NOBLOCK as many of the games are in small areas and you could end up with t's stuck together**

Features
* Climb
* Disco
* Maze
* Games Area
* S4S
* Pool
* Heal
* Couch Room
* Sandcastle 
* Gym Climb
* Sewers


Special Features
* There are secret spritetrails hidden around the map that use custom textures, (green and rainbows)
* A well designed Lockdown that locks each part of the prison down over a period of 2 minutes.
* A large sandcastle for the t's to play in
* A large sewer area for t's to rebel

Minor Bugs
* Unknown

The map is completely optimized and should not lag (tested with 40/40)

Testers -

Frazar
RogueSniper

Hi,

I have installed the following properties on the map ba_Jail_modern_mini.

Rooms:

- Healraum
- Armory & Small Control Room
- Small Pool
- Football field (Jard)
- Bulk Jail
- Kitchen

The following rooms weapons are hidden:

- Small pool in the pool in the lower right corner (P228)
(use the sofa to get to the bell) Massenjail on top of the camera -
- In two cells are weapons (P228) 1x and 1x top down
- In two cells are smoke grenades (1x 1x top down)

The following rooms have bay access:

- In two cells above 1x and 1x below.
- In the Healroom
- In the pool
- In the armory
- In Massenjail

In Massenjail still is a small separate room where a M249 and a bomb. The bomb can not be placed on the map.

On the map is an alarm system installed which can only be used by the counter terrorists. The doors all automatically. They are controlled by triggers. The armory door can only be used by the counter terrorists.

On the map there are 20 terrorists and 12 launch sites Counter terrorists launch sites.

The map ba_jail_modern_castle has been under production for a while. I'd like to point out that the map does have flaws in it. At its final stages, this was was rushed to a finish. Unforeseen circumstances occurred and caused the map to have a rough landing. 
This map was made for the Outbreak Community (http://outbreak-community.com/)

The map is optimized and should be able to run smoothly on any/most computers.

This map consists of:
Cell Block capable of holding 32 inmates (8x4cells)
"Ant Hills" around the map as "Healing Auras"(Medic)
A well equipped armoury
A large open space for ideas to spark in
Multiple Mini-games wired in
Splendid Scenery
Towers
Find out more when you play it




tl;dr

Map has some flaws/bugs (More visual and do not disrupt gamplay),
Extremely Playable
